OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain will
OL,6,Fspread northeast through the evening,
OL,7,Fheavy for a time. Becoming dry
OL,8,Fovernight with some clear spells but
OL,9,Fstaying cloudy towards Argyll and the
OL,10,FIsles.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FQuite cloudy to start but
OL,13,Fincreasingly bright or sunny weather
OL,14,Fdeveloping through the morning.
OL,15,FStaying dry and warm through the day.
